{"type": "article", "id": 23449, "title": "“植物”椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-08T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607185058KwAXhWQdqamz8rEk.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这把椅子来自俄罗斯女设计师 Lera Moiseeva，它的颜色和形态都指向生长中的植物。座位下面的“腿”朝着五个不同的方向，就像植物的根。圆形座位上连接着弯曲的钢铁座位靠背，让椅子显得轻盈。它是在“建立自然和设计之间的对话”题目下的设计，有墨绿色、黑色和白色三种，<a href=\"http://leramoiseeva.com/RAY-CHAIR\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071850559nA1QjKv2tJNrgVP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185057xbXT4gzcHRIs9ZY5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185057R50XoNI9raf8tB7b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185058gs7nkG9hCvQZc42a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00106838\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}